flowRoot.flowPara: Many people around the world will create sequences of colors. Of course! There might be many repeated sequences. But the less repeated sequence will be the winner! The winner sequence will earn $44.04 which will be
distributed between all the players who played this sequence. Imagine you
are the only one who played these sequence: you will receive all the prize!
